name: Bubblesuds
description:
LoRA for adding bubble suds as if stepping out of a bubble bath. This LoRA doesn't like clothes as most training images have the subjects in their birthday suits.

Trained for realistic models, but can work with anime models as well.

Recommended weights: 0.4 - 0.7

If you like this LoRA and wish to support me, consider buying me a beer at https://www.buymeacoffee.com/WaifuWizardWong 🍺 Your support is much appreciated!

Be sure to check out my other LoRAs!
